headline: JBLU Expands Global Reach With New Boston Routes to Barcelona and Milan
summary: JetBlue expands its Europe push with new Boston flights to Barcelona and Milan, aiming to capture more leisure travelers.

headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid EXPD and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Expeditors’s 22.7% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 9%, and its stock price has climbed to $139.22 per share. This was partly thanks to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
